This being very evident, there is no difficulty in the Second thing to be explained;
but we may eaſily tell what it is for theſe perſons to dwell, and lie down
together.

Princes and Governours ſhould ſtudy this, by making juſt, reaſonable, and merciful Laws;
and the people ſhould ſtudy it, by a humble ſubmiſſion to them, and careful obſervance
of them.

And next unto God are the Angelical Powers, who are the firſt Rayes from the firſt Light;
and ſparkle in no property ſo much as this: Settled quietneſs, and freedom from
Contention and Diſturbance.
